# Canvas → Google Calendar MCP Server

Syncs Canvas assignments/exams (incl. syllabus scan) to Google Calendar.

## Quick start

```bash
python -m venv .venv
# Windows
. .\.venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Configure Canvas
# Create .env next to server.py:
#   CANVAS_BASE_URL=https://your.canvas.domain.here 
#   CANVAS_API_TOKEN=YOUR_TOKEN

# Put Google "credentials.json" next to server.py (OAuth desktop file)
python server.py

